If you have had a pet lasting 6 weeks with no death of either yourself or of your pet, you are not engaging in any content that is non-trivial enough to require a slow proccing pet weapon in the first place.
<br />

<br />
You do not need a slow proc to kill light blues in "safe" zones or to farm green mobs.
<br />

<br />
The people who desire the slow proc are those who push the edge of mage solo power in difficult zones, or are in challenging groups that will be hard pressed without slow proc, and these people (raiders or not) certainly don't have pets that last for weeks, or even days...
<br />

<br />
Finraziel
<br />
Triton
<br />
Povar</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
